tutorialPages.messageText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "B3FD1B89490C304BA4185081677EF1B7", "Congratulations, you leveled up your first Crafting Profession! As you level up you\'ll be able to apply for higher certification ranks.")

NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "3188EBBD41F7717F54FA9E8C82C4E0F4", "At level 10 you can apply for your first Certification level: Apprentice. This will give you access to advanced crafting stations and stronger recipes.")
